<h2 id="credit-granted">Credit Granted</h2><p>Applicants may be eligible for up to 24 units (one semester) of credit for courses completed towards an incomplete AQF Level 9 or above qualification. In this Master of Applied Accounting and Master of Financial Management double masters, this limit applies to each degree separately.</p>
<h2 id="cognate-disciplines">Cognate Disciplines</h2><p>Accounting, actuarial studies, business, business information systems, economics, finance, international business, management, marketing, mathematics, public administration, statistics.</p>',
